# Code Modification Rules

## Markers

- Use '// ... existing code ...' to indicate unchanged sections
- Never omit markers when skipping code sections

## Line References

- Format: :endLine:filepath
- Severity: error

## Context

- Include only necessary surrounding lines for context
- Verify all necessary imports are included

## Directory Structure

- Check directory tree template before creating new files or directories
- Verify file location matches component type
- Maintain consistent directory hierarchy

## File Creation

- Check for duplicate files before creation
- Use file_search tool before creating new files
- Follow naming conventions
